    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Myriam Sfeir</title>
    <description>Myriam Sfeir is the assistant director of the Institute for Women’s Studies in the Arab World. Previously she served as senior managing editor of Al-Raida, the double-blind peer-reviewed journal published by IWSAW. She has worked on several groundbreaking issues of Al-Raida that dealt with various subjects considered taboo in the Arab world (sexuality, honor killings, incarcerated women, homosexuality).
</description>
